=== 1.1.1 / 2009-6-16
* Changed key size from 512 to 1024 to encrypt fields up to 117 bytes.
* Added rake task and module for recovering passwords given the root key.

=== 1.1.0 / 2009-6-8

* A completely new UI.
* Fixed user permissions bug.
* Encrypted password entry notes.
* Encrypted user password stored in the session cookie (now it's doubly-encrypted).
* Simplified password update screen for non-admin users.
* Numerous minor bug fixes.

=== 1.0.0 / 2008-12-16

* First release
